{"tid":645823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"rm-rf /* 立大功，Kuriko香港區域集體宕機","createTime":"2018-04-28T13:34:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T06:47:24.000Z","uid":135110,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"abb87210c1e7c7eb9ba0d386211457bcaf55c2ed","tid":645823,"uid":135110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T13:34:31.000Z","msg":"Kuriko又出大問題了，rm-rf/*又立大功了！ VPS 服務商 Kuriko 因 rm -rf /*，宿主機上所有數據丟失了。 Kuriko 4月24日在其官網刊登香港NAT區故障聲明，剛好你是Kuriko用戶，那麼你就得要動用你的佛系用戶精神了！<br />\n<br />\nVPS 服務商 Kuriko 因 rm -rf /*，宿主機上所有數據丟失了。 Kuriko 4月24日在其官網刊登香港NAT區故障聲明，內容如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/28/213301_d68cd51694d3669ba50d6141bd02809b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2F213301_d68cd51694d3669ba50d6141bd02809b.png&h=39fe0ee4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://kuriko.org/index.php/announcements/4/Kuriko-NAT.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkuriko.org%2Findex.php%2Fannouncements%2F4%2FKuriko-NAT.html&d=U4%2BlvUUDs5%2Fc0dKtW0k%2BnqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=abf37819\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kuriko.org/index.php/announcements/4/Kuriko-NAT.html</a><br />\n原文如下：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由於機房技術的rm -rf /*，導致目前宿主機上所有數據丟失，我們正在嘗試恢復原有數據以及獲取備份資料，但恢復可能較小。目前該區域所有主機處於OFFLINE中。<br />\n<br />\n我們將對所有至今日開通的月付用戶補償1自然月使用時長，將對半年付用戶補償2自然月使用賠償，預計5天內處理完成。<br />\n<br />\n如對處理結果不滿，請通過工單向我們反饋。<br />\n<br />\n非常抱歉給各位用戶造成的損失，KURIKO向各位道歉，感謝各位對KURIKO的支持與信賴。我們未來將進行定期數據備份保障各位用戶的數據安全，同時我們也會吸取本次教訓，杜絕重複事件的發生。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n題外話：rm -rf /*命令：刪除當前目錄下的所有文件的。然而以服務可靠，承諾會對每一位用戶的數據進行備份保證用戶數據安全的Kuriko，恐怕單憑一份故障聲明是無法平息一群用戶的怒火的了，人為因素在這個事件中的質疑聲響最大。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a9e3052704cc454b3bc1d8ea6b5de997b867b4","tid":645823,"uid":17510,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T19:04:22.000Z","msg":"乜撚野佛系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   用得咁撚夾硬真係好撚核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590a32b532c6bb5a08ca37ced3de68f271e4cac1","tid":645823,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T19:17:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606cfa887a149bb44e793a2797bc4caf0e7646e5","tid":645823,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T19:36:15.000Z","msg":"支那野？"},{"pid":"90c6049b0eb8821262f38b343b3e256dd576e4b0","tid":645823,"uid":61084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T21:03:50.000Z","msg":"之前gitlab 都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"511e7d228f4ae98b155a0b0bdb6a871c574e6001","tid":645823,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T21:08:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa101b46402672553d02a0d3443e542ab9c1cb51","tid":645823,"uid":100943,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T22:38:56.000Z","msg":"rm -rf /* 好似係由root directory剷起 唔係當前目錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60ae102a63bc0c2d992dd23c9aeeef32242acb0e","tid":645823,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa101b46402672553d02a0d3443e542ab9c1cb51","tid":645823,"uid":100943,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T22:38:56.000Z","msg":"rm -rf /* 好似係由root directory剷起 唔係當前目錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T22:58:50.000Z","msg":"直頭就係"},{"pid":"a347f5c3738e4b650eda1167a57de6f93d4d26df","tid":645823,"uid":135110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco